Dev Queue — Python/FastAPI backend
====================================

REST API for the Dev Queue learning tracker (Lab 7).

## Quick start

    pip install -r requirements.txt
    uvicorn main:app --reload --port 8000

Swagger UI → http://localhost:8000/docs
ReDoc      → http://localhost:8000/redoc

## Auth flow

1. POST /token  { "role": "ADMIN" }   → get a JWT (expires in 60 s)
2. Click "Authorize" in Swagger and paste the token
3. Call any endpoint

## Roles

| Role    | Permissions            |
|---------|------------------------|
| VISITOR | READ                   |
| WRITER  | READ, WRITE            |
| ADMIN   | READ, WRITE, DELETE    |

## Endpoints

### Auth
  POST /token

### Resources
  GET    /resources?limit=20&offset=0&status=queued&category=course
  GET    /resources/{id}
  POST   /resources
  PUT    /resources/{id}
  DELETE /resources/{id}     (requires DELETE permission)

### Folders (pipelines)
  GET    /folders?limit=20&offset=0
  GET    /folders/{id}
  POST   /folders
  PUT    /folders/{id}
  DELETE /folders/{id}       (requires DELETE permission — cascades folderId to null)
